85
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:24,210
How about you quiet down a little?

86
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:26,140
They say the weaker the dog,
the louder he barks!

87
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:28,080
What did you say!?

88
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:38,080
That's our Piccolo-san!

89
00:07:41,490 --> 00:07:43,160
S- Son!

90
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:45,500
Not too shabby, Piccolo!

91
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:50,840
W- what are you doing down here!?
Have you come back to Hell?

92
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:56,440
And after all the trouble I went
to sending you back to Earth!

93
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,110
W- what's this?

94
00:07:58,110 --> 00:08:01,270
It's okay, just shake my hand.

95
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:08,790
