125
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:30,580
We will now hold the Tenkaichi
Tournament Junior Championship Match!

126
00:11:32,890 --> 00:11:35,290
Son Goku-kun!

127
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:40,530
